    <item>
      <title>威尔士民族主义者结束对少数工党政府的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/welsh-nationalists-end-support-for-minority-labour-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威尔士民族主义政党 Plaid Cymru 终止了与权力下放的工党政府的合作协议，这对新任首席部长 Vaughan Gething 上任几周后造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/welsh-nationalists-end-support-for-minority-labour-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 14:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tennet Grid 交易陷入停滞，暴露了德国联盟的裂痕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/german-coalition-rifts-revealed-by-stalled-tennet-grid-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国未能敲定收购电网运营商 Tennet Holding BV 部分股份的交易，暴露了奥拉夫·肖尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 执政联盟内部新的分歧。]]></description>
